    "description": "Join the Niva Bupa South Asia Partners family as a Investment Banker in Varanasi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Niva Bupa South Asia Partners:\nNiva Bupa South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Ensure compliance with tax regulations and statutory requirements\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Niva Bupa South Asia Partners!",
